	<h1 class="title">「票房」《少年班》票房输这么多，不只因为吴京</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/system/users/faces/73/small/73.jpg?1415670876" alt="">
					</span>
				<span class="name">俞斯译 </span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2015-06-25 09:01:16 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/11219/medium/11219.jpg?1436641693" alt="" />			
	</div>
	<!-- 传入参数：obj(aritcle, paper, card, mob) -->


<div class="com-share" data-id="11219" data-title="《「票房」《少年班》票房输这么多，不只因为吴京》，来自@好奇心日报" data-pic="http://www.qdaily.com/system/articles/articleshows/11219/medium/11219.jpg?1436641693" data-url="http://www.qdaily.com/mobile/articles/11219.html" data-weiboAppkey="2462590045">
	<div class="share-bd clearfix">
